262→/// Convert tool schemas to OpenAI Responses API function-calling format.
263→///
264→/// Uses the flat format required by the Responses API where `name` is at top level:
265→/// ```json
266→/// { "type": "function", "name": "...", "parameters": {...}, "strict": true }
267→/// ```
268→///
269→/// This is the format used by OpenAI Codex and the Responses API.
270→///
271→/// Patches schemas for strict mode compliance:
272→/// - `additionalProperties: false` on all object schemas
273→/// - All properties included in `required` array
